at the chemical\ncompositions of GBs in Nb3Sn coatings for SRF cavities can be controlled by GB\nengineering and can be utilized to optimize fabrication of high-quality Nb3Sn\ncoatings for SRF cavities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 30 Jun 2019 21:41:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Feb 2020 21:32:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-24"}
