M) is used as the algorithm for pattern\nrecognition of different locations based on the samples taken from RSS and\nchannel estimation coefficients.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 30 Jun 2019 21:52:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-02"}
